# Profilo Designer — environment variables (OPTIONAL)
#
# This project needs NO backend and NO env vars to run.
# Copy this file to ".env" only if you later add integrations.
# In Vite, variables MUST start with VITE_ to be exposed to the app.
#
# Examples you might add in future:
# VITE_REGISTER_URL=https://live.holistichealervedika.com/
# VITE_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
VITE_API_BASE